                  <provenance>
                    Provenance: This codex was donated to Trinity Western University by Robert N. Thompson, who spent some years immediately following World War II in
                    Ethiopia working with the Ministry of Education. Later, he served with the mission organization, SIM (then “Sudan Interior Mission,” now “Serving In Ministry”).
                  </provenance>
